Global Laparoscopic Access Device Market Insights
Laparoscopic Access Device Market size was valued at USD 3.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7% from 2024 to 2030.

Laparoscopic Access Device Market Overview
The global laparoscopic access device market was valued at approximately USD 1.77 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 2.79 billion by 2029, exhibiting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.90% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by the increasing preference for minimally invasive surgeries, advancements in surgical technologies, and a rising number of surgical procedures worldwide. The market encompasses various devices such as suction or irrigation systems, robotic-assisted surgery systems, and closing devices, catering to applications in general surgery, gynecology, and other medical fields. The demand for these devices is further propelled by the growing prevalence of chronic diseases and an aging global population.

